high_descs: Turn left and walk to the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the red apple from inside the microwave and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the apple on the middle shelf inside the fridge, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the chilled apple inside the sink on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a sink.

high_descs: Take a step then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and grab the apple that's in there then close the door.
Move to your right until you face the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Move to your left until you're in front of the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the microwave across from you.
Pull the apple out of the microwave.
Go to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the apple on the second shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the apple to chill, then remove the apple from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and walk through the kitchen to the sink on your right.
Place the apple in the sink, to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the sink.
